Routes (Http Handlers)
Das Package Routes ruft die Methoden
des Charge Package auf und stellt die
Ergebnisse als REST Endpoints zur Verfügung.
+ AddContract(InsertContract): HttpHandler
+ UpdateContract(UpdateContract): HttpHandler
+ DeleteContract(DeleteContract): HttpHandler
+ AddRenter(InsertRenter): HttpHandler
+ UpdateRenter(UpdateRenter): HttpHandler
+ DeleteRenter(DeleteRenter): HttpHandler
+ AddLessor(InsertLessor): HttpHandler
+ UpdateLessor(UpdateLessor): HttpHandler
+ DeleteLessor(DeleteLessor): HttpHandler
+ AddObject(AddObject): HttpHandler
+ UpdateObject(UpdateObject): HttpHandler
+ DeleteObject(DeleteObject): HttpHandler
+ RecalculateContractPrice(UpdateContract): HttpHandler
+ GetContracts(GetContracts): HttpHandler
+ GenerateContract(GenerateContract): HttpHandler

POST /api/contract/add -> Routes.AddContract
PUT /api/contract/update -> Routes.UpdateContract
DELETE /api/contract/delete/{ID} -> Routes.DeleteContract
POST /api/renter/add -> Routes.AddRenter
PUT /api/renter/update -> Routes.UpdateRenter
DELETE /api/renter/delete/{ID} -> Routes.DeleteRenter
POST /api/lessor/add -> Routes.AddLessor

POST /api/object/add -> Routes.AddObject
PUT /api/object/update -> Routes.UpdateObject
DELETE /api/object/delete/{ID} -> Routes.DeleteObject
